Why Spotify Design System ?

We thought it was great for people, who like to design & to code to have this public library, in order to understand this brand and her application.

What about copyright ?

Except our original creations of interfaces, assets, icons, illustrations, everything belong to Spotify and if we are asked to take the website down, we will. No money is made whatsoever & it's purely fanmade.
